name: prairie gentian
description: photowork 3464x3464px. i love to take minimalistic photos of blossoms.  eustomia (prairie gentian) for me is one of the most elegant and charismatic flowers. it also stands for appreciation and gratitude. although it has such a delicate bloom, the whole plant knows how to endure rough time. i'm really fascinated by this flower and tried to be as careful as possible editing this fullframe photography, to keep her delicate character.
